      "span_text": "The cellular and molecular consequences of wnt signaling have been defined in some detail in epithelial stem cells and their progenitors, especially those of the colon.  The general scheme of the canonical wnt pathway is that the exposure of cells to wnt protein inhibits the intracellular degradation of ␤-catenin."
